---
// MethodologySection - The Zero Ad Spend Member System: 6 pillar cards
---

<section id="methodology" class="methodology-section">
  <div class="grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-badge">Our System</span>
      <h2>
        The 24/7 AI Member<br/>Appointment System
      </h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        An intelligent system that contacts, nurtures, and books your leads around the clock without your staff ever picking up the phone.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:zap" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Database Reactivation</h3>
        <p>We unlock revenue from your existing leads and past members that have gone cold. Instant cashflow from assets you already own, so the system pays for itself from day one.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:target" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Offer Positioning</h3>
        <p>Don't have an offer? We build one for you. Already have one? We refine it. Either way, we position your gym as the obvious choice in your market with the right message to the right people.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:bot" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Instant Speed-to-Lead</h3>
        <p>New lead comes in? Our AI responds within 60 seconds via text and voice. No more leads going cold because your staff was busy running a class.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:message-circle" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">04</span>
        </div>
        <h3>AI-Powered Nurture</h3>
        <p>Persistent, intelligent follow-up across text and voice. Our AI handles the 5-8 touchpoints needed to book an appointment, around the clock, every single day.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:calendar-check" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">05</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Automated Booking</h3>
        <p>Qualified prospects are booked directly onto your calendar. All you do is show up and welcome them. No chasing, no convincing, no phone tag.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-top">
          <div class="pillar-icon-wrap">
            <iconify-icon icon="lucide:bar-chart-3" class="pillar-icon"></iconify-icon>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-number">06</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Full Transparency</h3>
        <p>Real-time dashboard showing every lead, every conversation, and every booked appointment. You see exactly what's happening and what you're paying for.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .methodology-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .methodology-section { padding: 8rem 0; }
  }

  .grid-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--grid-line) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container { padding: 0 2rem; }
  }

  .section-header {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    background: var(--accent-bg);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  .pillar-card {
    background: var(--page-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .pillar-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-hover-border);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .pillar-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillar-icon-wrap {
    width: 3.5rem; height: 3.5rem;
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .pillar-card:hover .pillar-icon-wrap {
    border-color: var(--accent-hover-border);
  }

  .pillar-icon { color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.5rem; }

  .pillar-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--number-color);
  }

  .pillar-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pillar-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
